        <h1>Facebook Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">CSFrace - Web Scraping Application</p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>üìã Purpose:</strong> This page explains how to delete your Facebook data from CSFrace in compliance with Facebook's Platform Policy.
